163
00:07:49.386 --> 00:07:50.636
Ooh!

164
00:07:50.637 --> 00:07:52.138
We're gonna have lotsa
fun with this guy!

165
00:07:52.139 --> 00:07:54.390
You let that poor thing
go. you're hurting him!

166
00:07:54.391 --> 00:07:55.224
Huh?

167
00:07:55.225 --> 00:07:56.476
