168
00:07:57.603 --> 00:07:59.562
Let's go. Come on!

169
00:07:59.563 --> 00:08:01.147
[Hiroshi] Whoa. his
comb is really cool.

170
00:08:01.148 --> 00:08:02.732
You guys are a
bunch of brats. too!

171
00:08:02.733 --> 00:08:04.151
Yeah. that's right!

172
00:08:06.403 --> 00:08:07.904
