some weird chicken disease?

175
00:08:11.658 --> 00:08:12.783
Oh. right.

176
00:08:12.784 --> 00:08:13.868
[Brown Haired Boy]
I got an idea!

177
00:08:13.869 --> 00:08:15.703
How about we feed him to my cat?

178
00:08:15.704 --> 00:08:17.455
[Hiroshi] That'll be awesome!

179
00:08:17.456 --> 00:08:19.624
- (both chuckles)
- Koke!

180
00:08:19.625 --> 00:08:20.875
Hey. get back here!

181
00:08:20.876 --> 00:08:22.961
- [Hiroshi] Whoa!
- Stop trying to get away!

182
00:08:24.588 --> 00:08:27.174
<i>Don't waste my time.
you little punks!</i>

183
00:08:28.091 --> 00:08:29.800
Kokokokoko!

184
00:08:29.801 --> 00:08:31.970
Give it up. you damn chicken!

185
00:08:33.764 --> 00:08:35.181
