186
00:08:35.182 --> 00:08:36.600
Kokokokoko. koke!

187
00:08:42.272 --> 00:08:44.106
[Brown Haired Boy]
Hold it right there!

188
00:08:44.107 --> 00:08:45.274
Huh?

189
00:08:45.275 --> 00:08:46.360
Kokokokoko!

190
00:08:49.112 --> 00:08:50.613
Koke-ko.

191
00:08:50.614 --> 00:08:51.448
Oh.

192
00:08:53.909 --> 00:08:58.162
- Koko!
- (boys panting)

193
00:08:58.163 --> 00:08:59.497
What's going on?

194
00:08:59.498 --> 00:09:02.208
That's our rooster.
we're taking him back.

195
00:09:02.209 --> 00:09:03.085
Oh?

196
00:09:05.003 --> 00:09:05.796
Koko.

197
00:09:07.381 --> 00:09:09.674
