201
00:09:14.638 --> 00:09:17.390
How many times have I told
you not to leave the yard?

202
00:09:17.391 --> 00:09:19.559
<i>[Keiji] Mr. Cluckers?</i>

203
00:09:19.560 --> 00:09:20.518
