204
00:09:20.519 --> 00:09:22.562
We'll try to do better.

205
00:09:22.563 --> 00:09:25.231
(both grunting)

206
00:09:25.232 --> 00:09:26.816
Tsk! Let's get out of here!

207
00:09:26.817 --> 00:09:27.817
Yeah.

208
00:09:27.818 --> 00:09:28.652
Koke.

209
00:09:30.070 --> 00:09:31.988
(old man chuckles)

210
00:09:31.989 --> 00:09:34.616
<i>You saved my feathers. Old Man.</i>

211
00:09:38.620 --> 00:09:41.956
