that rooster is his?

212
00:09:41.957 --> 00:09:44.125
No way that bird belongs
to the old geezer.

213
00:09:44.126 --> 00:09:45.376
- he lied to us!
- My quota.

214
00:09:45.377 --> 00:09:46.211
My quota.

215
00:09:47.838 --> 00:09:48.881
I must reach it.

216
00:09:49.840 --> 00:09:51.340
Yes. sir.

217
00:09:51.341 --> 00:09:52.925
This month. yes.

218
00:09:52.926 --> 00:09:53.760
My quota.

219
00:09:55.179 --> 00:09:57.722
<i>Thanks for taking
care of me. Old Man.</i>

220
00:09:57.723 --> 00:10:01.225
<i>But I've got things to
do and places to go.</i>

221
00:10:01.226 --> 00:10:02.727
Koke.

222
00:10:02.728 --> 00:10:03.936
Sorry to say.

223
00:10:03.937 --> 00:10:05.856
This is all I have to offer you.

224
00:10:07.274 --> 00:10:09.942
<i>[Keiji] Brown rice.
corn and shiso leaves.</i>

225
00:10:09.943 --> 00:10:11.069
<i>You know what this is?</i>

226
00:10:12.404 --> 00:10:16.490
