special and bountiful feast!</i>

227
00:10:16.491 --> 00:10:17.658
(Keiji aggressively pecking)

228
00:10:17.659 --> 00:10:18.826
It's that good?

229
00:10:18.827 --> 00:10:20.828
I'm glad you're enjoying it.

230
00:10:20.829 --> 00:10:23.623
(Keiji aggressively pecking)

231
00:10:23.624 --> 00:10:24.458
Ah.

232
00:10:25.751 --> 00:10:26.585
Koke?

233
00:10:28.253 --> 00:10:30.963
I remember how my wife
would feed the sparrows

234
00:10:30.964 --> 00:10:32.549
