more time with her.

239
00:10:45.145 --> 00:10:47.813
{\an8}<i>♪ I'll be walking alone ♪</i>

240
00:10:47.814 --> 00:10:50.816
{\an8}<i>♪ For lonely long time ♪</i>

241
00:10:50.817 --> 00:10:52.235
<i>[Old Woman] No need to fight!</i>

242
00:10:52.236 --> 00:10:53.486
<i>There's enough for everyone.</i>

243
00:10:53.487 --> 00:10:54.654
<i>There.</i>

244
00:10:54.655 --> 00:10:56.406
<i>Don't eat too fast.
now. (chuckles).</i>

245
00:10:59.785 --> 00:11:01.953
{\an8}<i>♪ Searching for the answers ♪</i>

246
00:11:01.954 --> 00:11:06.291
{\an8}<i>♪ But where am I
supposed to go ohh ♪</i>

247
00:11:08.126 --> 00:11:10.920
And here I am.
talking your ear off.

248
00:11:10.921 --> 00:11:13.130
Somehow I feel
comfortable with you

249
00:11:13.131 --> 00:11:14.758
like I could tell you anything.

250
00:11:16.093 --> 00:11:18.928
<i>[Keiji] I understand what
you're saying. Old Man.</i>

251
00:11:18.929 --> 00:11:21.682
<i>I should've spent more
